@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gwacct(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.cos(tmp)
    v2 = v0
    tmp = (wp.cos(v2) + v2)
    v2 = 0.60
    v2 = (wp.sin(0.86) + (wp.cos(v0 + 0.93) / 0.02))
    v0 = (wp.sin((v2 + 0.39 - tmp + 0.96)) - wp.sin(wp.exp(v2 + 0.31)))
    v1 = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.64) * (v2 + 0.80 / v0 + 0.87)) - (wp.sin(v2 + 0.81) / v0))
    data[tid] = v0
